Hello! It's nice to learn more about your skills. As we discussed earlier, you're an advanced data analyst with expertise in Python, Java, JavaScript, Machine Learning, Big Data, and Power BI.

In my memory, I recall that you're also proficient in developing scalable RESTful APIs using Express.js for backend development and optimizing database queries for improved API response times. Additionally, you've worked on various projects such as designing a secure authentication system with role-based access and token-based security and creating a robust system architecture to handle high traffic.

I'm confident that your skills will be a great asset in the data analysis field. Keep working hard, and I'm sure you'll continue to excel in this area!

Do you have any specific questions about your skills or experiences?
